      "title": "The Dirac operator and gamma matrices for quantum Minkowski spaces",
      "abstract": "Gamma matrices for quantum Minkowski spaces are found. The invariance of the corresponding Dirac operator is proven. We introduce momenta for spin 1/2 particles and get (in certain cases) formal solutions of the Dirac equation."
